{
  "stem": "19550.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You, as I said, you know, nothing exists either in reality, or emotionally, or mentally, except that, that pain, that urge, that, that readiness to or to fall upon anything that you can put into your mouth.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know whether or not in my case, or for that matter, the case of the camps that I was in, is typical at all or in any way, you know, worse than in other places, it was in other places.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to remember that we were a relatively valued group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were hired out originally to [INAUDIBLE], which was responsible for the manufacturing to the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we had Air Force, an Air Force group that was supervising us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were, by no means, many of them as bad as the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the first place, they don't consider themselves guards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were guarding the interest of the Air Force and of getting the fuselages done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The SS would be beyond the perimeter of the camp, usually.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They guarded the camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But once we went to work and we were put down into the mine, there were maybe one or two SS men around.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were basically working under Air Force and [INAUDIBLE] supervision.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, we, they erected a special tent where they tortured him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would not let him die for a whole week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all week long this horrible, inhuman shriek and cry was emanating from that, from that tent.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the most horrible experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we with it went our impotence, our inability to do anything for him or about him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm at it again, we tried to figure out how we could somehow manage to get some food to him, or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
